definitions.definition: A nonsense word commonly used in YouTube Poop by playing an audio clip forward and in reverse consecutively ; said in reference to this editing style , and to describe palindromes and humorously symmetrized images.

main_definition: ( Internet slang , humorous , nonce word ) A nonsense word commonly used in YouTube Poop by playing an audio clip forward and in reverse consecutively ; said in reference to this editing style , and to describe palindromes and humorously symmetrized images.
